HEADWORD: Aventine
<hw>Av"en*tine</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to
<ets>Mons Aventinus</ets>, one of the seven hills on which Rome
stood.</def> <rj><au>Bryant.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
