HEADWORD: Aventine
<hw>Av"en*tine</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A post of security or
defense.</def> <mark>[Poetic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Into the castle's tower,⟦br⟧
